    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Since you haven't specified any plans for further processing the String, you can use something like this to find uppercase and digits:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class Extraction {\n\n  public static void main(String[] args) {\n    String test = \"This is a test containing S and 10\";\n    for (char c : test.toCharArray()) {\n        if (Character.isDigit(c)) {\n            System.out.println(\"Digit: \" + c);\n        }\n        else if (Character.isUpperCase(c)) {\n            System.out.println(\"Uppercase letter: \" + c);\n        }\n    }\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
